                            "text": "Disabled people work in many capacities as health care professionals. It is important they can meet the competencies and have the support and reasonable adjustments they need. If you are not sure about a studentâ€™s ability to meet competencies you can discuss any concerns with the disability team and regulatory bodies.",
                            "space_after": true
