                    "subtitle": "Summary",
                    "components": [
                        {
                            "type": "text-paragraph",
                            "text": "It is important that students with disabilities are notified of their placement in good time so they can make adequate preparations. Some students with disabilities may need time to agree reasonable adjustments or discuss their learning needs prior to the placement"
